// An if/else whose arms converge at a code block, followed by an unconditional infinite loop
// with no exit. Nothing reaches a sink in the original CFG, so an impossible edge is added at
// the deepest unvisited node (4) and post-domination cascades back through 3, 1, 2, and 0.
// Structuring then emits the if/else, the converged code block, and the trailing loop in
// sequence.
//
//       0
//      / \
//     1   2
//      \ /
//       3
//       |
//    -> 4
//   |   |
//    ---

cond,0,1,2
code,1,3
code,2,3
code,3,4
code,4,4
